'''Domain Steng''' was one of the early [[Domain]]s among the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. During the [[Cremlevian War]], the Domain was led by [[Steng]], the first [[Warmaster]]. They were one of the most powerful Domains among the Yuuzhan Vong. They battled with [[Domain Yo'gand]] for control of the [[Yuuzhan Vong galaxy]]. Eventually, the Domain was driven to [[Ygziir]], where they dug in. [[Yo'gand]], the leader of the rival Domain, eventually destroyed Ygziir by dropping its moon onto the planet, in what became known as [[Yo'gand's Core]]. Domain Steng either surrendered or was wiped out.

